<div class="steps" markdown="1">

1.  Make the [HTML Source][docu-source-source] view active by clicking within
    it or pressing the <kbd>Tab</kbd> key until it is selected.

2.  The HTML Source pane is a standard Mac OS X text editor.

3.  You can observe the effects of your edits to the Tidy’d document in the
    [Tidy’d HTML pane][doc-view_tidyd] and in the
    [Tidy Messages][docwin-messages] table.

